channel.title: Huge problem, need an expert(im being hacked)
channel.description:
Hey guys, My ip is all screwed up, and I think someone hacked it. Im unsure of what they did.
I go to my server wont let me in, I changed the ip to 127.0.0.1 and I got in fine.
Next i tryed my regulor ip adress, instead of my no-ip to see if that was the problem.
It wouldnt let me into my regulor ip adress. I had no problem till this day, with any of this. And im starting to get worried that this is only the start of the hackers fun... Please help me!
-Will
